Detailed Description

template<typename EvalT, typename Traits>
class Aeras::XZScalarAdvectionResid< EvalT, Traits >

XZScalarAdvection equation Residual for atmospheric modeling.

This evaluator computes the residual of the XZScalarAdvection equation for atmospheric dynamics.
